description: Try our easy to follow Seafood Spring Rolls recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Spring rolls,Deep fryer,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Seafood,Sesame free,Christmas,Soy free,Wheat free,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Seafood Spring Rolls Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 2 tbs stir fry sauce sweet chilli

recipeInstructions.text: Combine all of the above ingredients except spring roll pastry in a large bowl and mix well.

Place a sheet of pastry on a flat surface, top with 1 tablespoon of mixture then roll once. Tuck ends in then continue rolling. Brush ends with a little water to seal, then repeat with remaining rolls.
Deep fry in hot oil until golden (about 3â€“4 minutes) then serve with additional sweet chilli marinade, fresh lettuce and herbs.
